        FlowBuilder<?> getFlowBuilder​(java.lang.String namespace,

        Obtains a FunctionBuilder registered with this OfficeBuilder.

        This enables addition configuration of ManagedFunction instances registered by a ManagedObjectSource.

        Parameters:

        functionName - Name of the ManagedFunction.
        Returns:
